  "body": "### Description\n\nI'm interested in creating a Vert.x server that updates TLS certificates without restarts using the new Vert.x feature implemented in https://github.com/eclipse-vertx/vert.x/commit/f288f356bcdd9a03273cd1bb9c46b9a720d604c6 and documented at https://vertx.io/docs/vertx-core/java/#_updating_ssltls_configuration\r\n\r\nThe feature is available with Vertx 4.4 but the current Vertx version for Quarkus is 4.3.\n\n### Implementation ideas\n\nUpgrade vertx to 4.4.2",
